media_tile_777233576.text: One headset for all your devices. Take the G633 from your gaming rig to your gaming console, your mobile devices, or anywhere else. The G633 works with PC, mobile, and game consoles, including PS4â„¢ and Xbox Oneâ„¢.Virtual 7.1 Surround only on PC and requires use of USB connection. media_tile_842265300.text: G633 has two customizable LIGHTSYNC lighting zones: The light strips and logos. Each zone can each be programmed separately from approx. 16.8 million colors, or with different animations and effects. They can also synchronized with other LIGHTSYNC devices. Use LGS to personalize lighting to match your rig, your gear and your style.Advanced features requires Logitech Gaming Software and USB.

media_tile_1548322686.text: Assign custom commands using LGS on the three programmable G-keys for a seamless gaming and media experience. Set custom controls to control your audio profiles, skip to the next song, activate push-to-talk communication, trigger instant in-game command combinations, and more.Advanced features requires Logitech Gaming Software and USB.

media_tile_154832268.text: Customize audio settings and create personal sound profiles for each game you play. Use LGS to program the audio equalizer and store pre-set audio profiles for games, music, and movies.Advanced features requires Logitech Gaming Software and USB.

media_tile_154832268_21318611.text: Donâ€™t stop in the middle of a game to take a call. Answer it and keep on playing. Answer calls, play music and communicate in-game without having to pause the game or take your eyes off the action. G633 features one USB connection and one analog input that connects and mixes sound from up to two devices.

media_tile_154832268_814155154.text: Ensure you are heard with a crystal-clear and noise-cancelling boom mic. The boom has an indicator LED so you know when your microphone is on mute. When not in use, the noise-cancelling boom mic can be folded back into the headphones and is nearly invisible. G633 also includes mobile cable and secondary inline mic for mobile devices.

media_tile_154832268_1593155026.text: G633 not only includes advanced features and performance, it is designed to be extremely comfortable for long gaming sessions. Sports mesh materials used in the ear cups and headband are soft and breathable for maximum comfort. G633 is fitted with our largest-diameter ear pads to fit completely around the ears with no direct pressure on soft tissues and passive noise isolation. To keep your headset clean, you can remove and handwash the ear cups.
